### Convert JSON to XML
POST http://localhost:8080/convert/json-to-xml
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/xml

{
  "name": "Alice",
  "age": 30
}

###

### Convert XML to JSON
POST http://localhost:8080/convert/xml-to-json
Content-Type: application/xml
Accept: application/json

<user>
    <name>Alice</name>
    <age>30</age>
</user>

###

### Fetch JSON from URL and convert to XML
POST http://localhost:8080/convert/fetch-json-to-xml
Content-Type: text/plain
Accept: application/xml

https://jsonplaceholder.typicode.com/users/1

###

### Fetch XML from URL and convert to JSON
POST http://localhost:8080/convert/fetch-xml-to-json
Content-Type: text/plain
Accept: application/json

https://www.w3schools.com/xml/simple.xml
